Source: grml-desktop
Section: grml
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Michael Prokop <mika@grml.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 5)
Standards-Version: 3.7.2

Package: grml-desktop
Architecture: any
Depends: idesk
Suggests: fluxbox, fvwm | fvwm2 | fvwm-crystal, ion2, ion3, pekwm
Conflicts: grml-etc (< 0.9.14)
Description: configuration files for the X desktop at grml
 This packages provides several configuration files for
 different tools and window managers used at grml. The
 files have been separated from package grml-etc to
 make customization of grml easier.
